Package: foregen
Type: Package
Title: foregen - (fo)recast (re)gressor (gen)erator
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Willy", "Hardy", email = "wjhrdy@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: It makes a data.frame that can be input into the xreg
    argument as used in the forecast package. Also has 2 functions to help in creating
    regressors from a table of events.
